{"word":"ἀνήκω","slug":"ἀνήκω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n8622\" key=\"a)nh/kw\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἀνήκω</orth>, <sense id=\"n8622.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to have come up to</tr_> a point, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">reach up to,</tr_> of persons and things, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐς μέτρον τινὸς ἀ.</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:127\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.127</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">αἱμασιὴν ὕψος ἀνήκουσαν ἀνδρὶ ἐς τὸν ὀμφαλόν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:60\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.60</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐς τὰ μέγιστα ἀ. ἀρετῆς πέρι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:49\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.49</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">χρήμασι ἀ. ἐς τὰ πρῶτα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:134\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.134</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">φρενῶν ἐς τὰ ἐμεωυτοῦ πρῶτα οὔκω ἀ.</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">have</tr_> not yet <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">reached</tr_> the highest point I aim at, ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:13\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\